name: Add Product In Cart Page
description: As a User I want to Add Product In Cart Page

children.name: User Check  Add Product In Cart Page
Given I Launch browser
And I Navigate to url "http://automationexercise.com/"
Then I Verify that home page is visible successfully
When I Click on Products button
And I Hover over first product and click 'Add to cart'
And I Click Continue Shopping button
And I Hover over second product and click 'Add to cart'
And I Click View Cart button
Then Verify both products are added to Cart
And I Verify their prices, quantity and total price
User VerifyProduct quantity in cart
Given I Launch browser
And I Navigate to url "http://automationexercise.com/"
Then I Verify that home page is visible successfully
When I Click on View Product
Then I Verify product detail is opened
And I Increase quantity to '4'
And I Click Add to cart button
And I Click View Cart button
Then I Verify that product is displayed in cart page with exact quantity
User Remove Product From cart
Given I Launch browser
And I Navigate to url "http://automationexercise.com/"
Then I Verify that home page is visible successfully
When I Hover over first product and click 'Add to cart'
And I Click View Cart button
Then I Verify that cart page is displayed
And I 'X' button corresponding to particular product
Then Verify that product is removed from the cart
User Add to Cart from Recommended items

When I Scroll down to footer

name: Add View Category Products page

children.name: User Check View Category Products page

Then I Verify that user is navigated to brand page and brand products are displayed

User Check Add review on Product
Given I Launch browser
And I Navigate to url "http://automationexercise.com/"
Then I Verify that home page is visible successfully
When I Click on Products button
Then I Verify user is navigated to ALL PRODUCTS page successfully

name: Check out Page

children.name: User Verify Address details in checkOut page
